<p class="p">The emulsifying activity index (EAI) and stability index (ESI) of RSP were determined following the method of Liu, Shim, Poth, and Reaney (
 <xref rid="fsn3936-bib-0026" ref-type="ref" class="xref">2016</xref>). Briefly, freshly prepared RSP solution (2% in DI water, w/v) was mixed with soybean oil at a ratio of 3:1 (v/v), followed by homogenization using a homogenizer (FA25 Model, Fluko Equipment Co. Ltd., Shanghai, China) at 44,000 
 <italic class="italic">g</italic> for 1 min to prepare the emulsion. After 15 min, the emulsion was diluted 1,000‐fold with 0.1% SDS (w/v) and the absorbance at 500 nm was recorded. The EAI and ESI were calculated using the following equations: 
 <disp-formula id="fsn3936-disp-0004" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">(4)</label>
  <math id="nlm-math-11" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mtext class="mtext">EAI</mtext>
    <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mo stretchy="false" class="mo">(</mo>
     <msup class="msup">
      <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">m</mi>
      <mn class="mn">2</mn>
     </msup>
     <mo stretchy="false" class="mo">/</mo>
     <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">g</mi>
     <mo stretchy="false" class="mo">)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo class="mo">=</mo>
    <mfrac class="mfrac">
     <mrow class="mrow">
      <mn class="mn">2</mn>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mo class="mo">×</mo>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mn class="mn">2.303</mn>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mo class="mo">×</mo>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <msub class="msub">
       <mi class="mi">A</mi>
       <mn class="mn">0</mn>
      </msub>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mo class="mo">×</mo>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mi class="mi">V</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow class="mrow">
      <mn class="mn">10</mn>
      <mo class="mo">,</mo>
      <mn class="mn">000</mn>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mo class="mo">×</mo>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mi class="mi">φ</mi>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mo class="mo">×</mo>
      <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
      <mi class="mi">c</mi>
     </mrow>
    </mfrac>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
 <disp-formula id="fsn3936-disp-0005" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">(5)</label>
  <math id="nlm-math-12" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mtext class="mtext">ESI</mtext>
    <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mo stretchy="false" class="mo">(</mo>
     <mtext class="mtext">min</mtext>
     <mo stretchy="false" class="mo">)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo class="mo">=</mo>
    <mfrac class="mfrac">
     <msub class="msub">
      <mi class="mi">A</mi>
      <mn class="mn">0</mn>
     </msub>
     <mrow class="mrow">
      <msub class="msub">
       <mi class="mi">A</mi>
       <mn class="mn">0</mn>
      </msub>
      <mo class="mo">−</mo>
      <msub class="msub">
       <mi class="mi">A</mi>
       <mn class="mn">15</mn>
      </msub>
     </mrow>
    </mfrac>
    <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
    <mo class="mo">×</mo>
    <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
    <mi class="mi">t</mi>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
